        "customfield_12310192": "Corrected problems with GraphiteSink not having proper format in point tags. Format v1.1 suggests point tags should be delimited with ';' rather than '.' and also appear at the end of the metric name, not in the middle. Also removed risk of point tag value having empty space (will be replaced by '_').",
